title: SVENGOOLIE The Mummy's Curse (1944) Lon Chaney Jr. 12-9-17
description:
Chicago's Svengoolie Presents: "The Mummy's Curse", the Fifth film in the Universal series, and the 3rd and final to Feature Lon Chaney Jr. as Kharis. 
Also featuring Virginia Christine as Princess Ananka, who cleans up very nicely and unless you already know, you'll be surprised who she plays later on in her career.

PLOT: An irrigation project in the rural bayous of Louisiana unearths living mummy Kharis, who was ( SPOILER EDITED ) twenty-five years earlier.

Again, I used a Dvd print ( for better film quality) with Sven edited in appropriately. The original air date for this was 12-09-2017.
The episode features a interview with artist Alex Cross and a lot of old Sven skits because the films running time is about an hour.

Enjoy and requests are Welcome !! Unfortunately, Pirate Bay doesn't have a notification system for messages, so yours may go unread for some time. I'll try my best to keep up.

whodude33
